                     <title xml:lang="en">Sefer ha-terumah</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">ספר התרומה</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The enumeration of the dinim begins on folio 1r, but breaks of in the middle of no. 50 on folio 8v. The remaining dinim have been prefixed to the respective halakhot.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folios 278-280, which originally were not part of the present manuscript, contain a short treatise on sheḥiṭah and Seder rabenu Gershom. These pieces were apparently added as a substitute for the dinim of section 1 and 2 of the Sefer ha-terumah.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
